# SDLC (Software Development Lifecycle) Observability!
## Tracing Artifacts from Dev to Prod through all Pipelines

From the [Dynatrace Doc on Pipeline Observability](https://docs.dynatrace.com/docs/deliver/pipeline-observability-sdlc-events): People often say, "You can't manage what you can't measure." This principle holds especially true for the software development lifecycle. Pipeline observability is the practice of capturing telemetry data across the entire lifecycle to gain actionable insights and calculate key delivery metrics â€” as illustrated in the figure below.

![](data:image/png;base64,)

Click here to see the full [Software Development Lifecycle Dashboards](https://wkf10640.apps.dynatrace.com/ui/apps/dynatrace.dashboards/dashboard/4bd4a399-b2b9-4038-adf0-840ef8d4fbce#vfilter_Application=3420b2ac-f1cf-4b24-b62d-61ba1ba8ed05*&vfilter_Build=3420b2ac-f1cf-4b24-b62d-61ba1ba8ed05*&vfilter_Verison=3420b2ac-f1cf-4b24-b62d-61ba1ba8ed05*&from=now%28%29-24h&to=now%28%29) to experience how to get artifact lifecycle observability across multiple environments from multiple tools (CI,CD,Testing...)



---


## Introduction to SDLC Events

![](https://marvel-b1-cdn.bc0a.com/f00000000236551/dt-cdn.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/pipeline_observability_and_events-768x392.png)

Read more in the blog [Observability through the Software Development Lifecycle](https://www.dynatrace.com/news/blog/observability-throughout-the-software-development-lifecycle/)

### Where to Start: A Primer on SDLC Events (Dynatrace Doc)
* [What SDLC Events are defined?](https://docs.dynatrace.com/docs/discover-dynatrace/references/semantic-dictionary/model/sdlc-events)
* [How to Ingest SDCL Events from your DevOps Tools?](https://docs.dynatrace.com/docs/deliver/pipeline-observability-sdlc-events/sdlc-events)
* [Analytics Examples](https://docs.dynatrace.com/docs/deliver/pipeline-observability-sdlc-events/pipeline-observability-analyze)

### Ingesting SDLC Events from Argo, GitHub, GitLab, Azure DevOps ... (GitHub Repos)

On GitHub we have ready made OpenPipeline configurations, Dashboards and instructions for

| [Argo Sync Observability](https://github.com/Dynatrace/dynatrace-configuration-as-code-samples/tree/main/argocd_observability) | [GitHub Pipeline Observability](https://github.com/Dynatrace/dynatrace-configuration-as-code-samples/tree/main/github_pipeline_observability) | [GitLab Observability](https://github.com/Dynatrace/dynatrace-configuration-as-code-samples/tree/main/gitlab_pipeline_observability) | [Azure DevOps](https://github.com/Dynatrace/dynatrace-configuration-as-code-samples/tree/main/azure_devops_observability)

### More to come

There are more out-of-the-box configurations coming but nothing holds you back in sending SDLC events to Dynatrace already

**Got questions or feedback?**: [devrel@dynatrace.com](mailto:devrel@dynatrace.com?subject=SDLC%20Events%20Getting%20Started)

# Digging into SDLC Events

Lets analyze those events
